[ Win32 ]

To build everything:

   nmake -f NMakefile

To run the little test suite:

   nmake -f NMakefile test

[ Linux ]

To build everything:

    make

To run the little test suite:

    make test

The "appear" program is for 15-char sequences, "appear2" for 2-char
sequences, and "appear1" for 1-char sequences.

-agentzh


